Usage of Makefile

make -- build all
make short_tasks - build short tasks and their dependencies
make long_tasks - make long tasks and their dependencies
make style - astyle all sources from current directory and all its direct subdirectories
make clean - clean all .o, .d, .orig and executables


Common exit codes:

0 All was successful.
1 Error (re)allocating memory
2 Failed to open file
3 Unreachable code
10 Wrong number of parameters
11 Unknown parameter
12 Expected parameter
13 Too many parameters
Additional info may be printed to stderr.
